<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://app.mfa.gov.sg/data/paris/statements/REMARKS_FOR_MEDEF_28_Aug_08.html" class="external free" title="http://app.mfa.gov.sg/data/paris/statements/REMARKS_FOR_MEDEF_28_Aug_08.html" rel="nofollow">http://app.mfa.gov.sg/data/paris/statements/REMARKS_FOR_MEDEF_28_Aug_08.html</a> SPEECH BY SINGAPORE AMBASSADOR TO FRANCE, HIS EXCELLENCY BURHAN GAFOOR AT MEDEF UNVERSITE DEBATE AT L'ECOLE POLYTECHNIQUE, 28 AUGUST 2008</li>
